content: Guard the greatest secrets in Hyrule – or your budding social life – safely by writing them in the Zelda Triforce journal. This handmade journal sports a distinguished leather cover and is accented with a classy Triforce image any Zelda fan will love.

The miniature petting zoo is open for business thanks to these tiny crochet animals. These impossibly cute little critters span the entire animal kingdom from domestic animals like dogs and cats to more exotic species like the elusive narwhal.

He may be useless as a Pokemon but as a fashion accessory you won’t find a better choice than Magikarp. This hand crocheted Pokemon hat displays all his fishy glory – just pray he doesn’t decide to evolve while you’re wearing him on your head.

Transform your little bundle of joy into an adorable little henchman by dressing him in the crocheted baby minion costume. Handcrafted with love in every stitch, it features a vivid blue bottom complemented by a brightly colored beanie in the form of a minion head.

Mr. Vincent Vega and Jules Winnefield are back from the dead – sort of – and ready to do your bidding. With hair that’ll put Elvis to shame, these <del>bad motherfuckers</del> Pulp Fiction taxidermy rats come dressed in their finest suits whilst packing heat.

Have some fun with your growing baby bump by sporting this peeking baby maternity shirt. Available in a variety of colors and both genders, the creative design shows your unborn fetus peeking their little head from the zip-fastener in your stomach.

titleEN: Star Wars AT-AT Walker Ear Plugs
content: Straight from the frozen battlefields of Hoth, the Star Wars AT-AT walker ear plugs have made their way to our Earth to provide some geeky flair for your outfit. Perfect for the oppressive Imperialist, these stainless steel plugs are made to order in various sizes.

Craft a one of a kind costume that’ll astonish and terrify by topping it off with one of these paper mache animal masks. The expertly crafted masks comes accented with pieces of hair and fur for added realism, in both a male and female form.

Vanquish your junk mail and credit card statements with one fell swoop of the Zelda Master Sword letter opener. This double edged letter opener has been expertly crafted to resemble the sword from Ocarina of Time and features its own stone base.

Get into the holiday spirit without actually having to wear a hideous holiday garment by baking up a batch of ugly Christmas sweater cookies. Baked with love in every kitschy sweater pattern, these Christmas treats are the perfect companion to a hot cup of cocoa.

Ring in the festival of lights in prehistoric style with the T-Rex Hanukkah Menorah. While your more religiously conservative family members might scoff at you, this golden ‘Manorasaurus Rex’ will make the holiday season one to remember.

Who’d ever thought having your foot chomped on by a great white could feel so good? Once this handmade shark sock latches its yarn teeth around you and envelops your feet in its cozy innards, you’ll never want him to let go.

Place a touch of magic in any room with the Harry Potter 3D wall letters. The letters come designed in the classic Potter font seen plastered across each book cover and also feature the classic jagged lightning accents to provide a truly authentic look.

The octopus necklace – also know as the jewel of the deep – is a handcrafted piece so stunning it’s fit for underwater royalty. This completely customizable necklace features an intricate design of colorful octopus tentacles that complement any look.

Prove you’re the ultimate G.O.T fan by ‘inking’ your body with a Game Of Thrones temporary tattoos. This detailed piece goes on with minimal pain and proudly displays the Stark family’s signature words surrounded by details pertaining to their adventures.

Let the world know you and your sweetheart are officially off the market by branding each other with the personalized stacking rings. If there’s a special someone you always want with you, these stylized rings are ideal – and a lot less permanent than tattoos.

Make those long work hours go by faster by entertaining yourself with the iridescence of the bismuth crystal. Each crystal features its own unique blend of colors while featuring a low melting point that allows you to alter the crystal’s physical appearance.

Channel your spirit party animal while raising the roof with the rainbow light up bear hood. You’ll light up the dance floor the moment you walk in and the ultra bright LEDs built into the faux fur begin lighting up in brilliant colors and patterns.

Bring some whimsy into the stuffy I.T. office environment by decorating your cubicle with some internet masterpieces. What better way to capture the essence of the internet than a gun-totting ninja kitty riding a fire-breathing unicorn with laser vision.

Take your origami skills to frightening heights by learning how to craft a cardboard skull mask. The easy to follow instructions provide a step by step guideline to transform a regular piece of paper or cardboard into a spooky skeleton mask.

Summon the benevolent beast of the deep whenever you desire a little candlelit company with the Godzilla shadow caster. When placed next to a candle, this pint sized reptile casts a larger than life shadow to create the illusion the legendary Godzilla has arrived.

Use furniture to play your favorite Nintendo games by decorating your room with the functional NES controller coffee table. This handmade gem gives the room a unique retro feel while allowing you to actually hook it up to your NES for unparalleled levels of gameplay.

Add a touch of whimsy to your room’s decor with the Beauty and the Beast clock. Styled after the Beast’s tightly wound  butler, Cogsworth, this jubilant wooden clock makes an ideal peace for brightening up your children’s room.

Get your little princess into cosplay from an early age by transforming her into video game royalty with the Princess Zelda crochet costume. This darling ensemble is hand tailored and can be worn by children ranging from ages 2-4.

Give the game room some great ambient lighting with the LEGO Super Mario Bros lamp. This retro LEGO lamp features an old school 8-bit graphic depicting the famous Italian plumbers heroically chasing after a mushroom and flower on their quest to power up.

Enlist the aid of the world’s best cook by prepping your meals using the Heisenberg cutting board. This one of a kind kitchen accessory is made using durable bamboo wood and comes decorated with an image of Walter White’s iconic alter ego on the board’s surface.

Commemorate the coolest President ever to <del>get serviced</del> serve with the epic Bill Clinton poster. This contemporary masterpiece depicts our 42nd President kicking ass and taking names all while looking like a rockstar.

Give the children some irreparable psychological damage by having them sleep with the Pinhead doll. This Hellraiser inspired doll comes skillfully decorated like a miniature version of the dreaded hell spawn leader of the Cenobites.

Butch up any room in your home by accenting it with the comfy boxing glove bean bag chair. Styled like an old-school leather boxing glove, this ginormous bean bag makes the perfect place for any boxing enthusiast to relax and unwind after a rigorous sparring session.

Satisfy your craving for <del>brains</del> sweets by taking a big chomp out of a zombie sugar cookie. These custom treats are baked fresh to order and come decorated like brain-thirsty zombies complete with blood, scars and a ton of sugar – yum!

Compliment your costume party with the perfect spooky treats by serving up some psychedelic chocolate skulls. These creepy treats are shaped like miniature skulls with half their cranium cut off exposing their savory and sugary braaaaaaains.

Lord Of The Rings fans look no further than the Hobbit bag for the ultimate way to store all your geeky gear. This hand carved and painted leather bag features a design inspired by the round door at Bag End complete with Gandalf’s Rune.

Give some new life to one of your favorite gaming devices by lighting the room up with the Nintendo console lamp. This geeky light source utilizes the classic NES console and its controllers to create a fixture that any gamer would approve of.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Soda Bottles
content: Create a lively nighttime environment at the old homestead simply by using some glow in the dark soda bottles for some mood lighting. The glass soda bottles are styled like the classic coke bottles of yesteryear and emit a vibrant glow perfect for parties.

Prepare for the apocalypse by practicing your zombie slaying skills on the zombie pinata. Designed to look like a terrifying zombie, Mr. Chompie comes dressed in a dashing shirt and jean combo that he accents with a stylish noose so you can beat him while he hangs.

Power up your bedroom with the equally comfortable and geektastic retro Nintendo bed set.  Inspired by the original 1980s Nintendo gaming machine, this geeky bedspread morphs your traditional bed into a giant old school multiplayer console.

If you’re the type that loves poking the eyes out of people in pictures, you’ll go nuts for the creepy baby doll head lights. These re-purposed doll heads emit an eerily soothing glow ideal for creating a hauntingly pleasant environment at your next  Halloween party.

Top your morning cup of Joe with some humor by stirring it with the coffee drinker’s spoon. This vintage piece of silverware comes custom stamped with a short comical phrase designed to brighten up those drab weekday mornings.

Experience the finer things in life by digging into one of these gourmet seven layer s’mores. Roasted and infused with real smoke, these handcrafted treats are the ultimate sinful snack while you lounge around by an open fire.

Become the envy of the office by transforming your workstation into an awe inspiring light show with the light up cube. This compact cube emits a bevy of wonderful and vivid hues that can be customized to match your style or mood.

Reminisce over your greatest defeats and triumphs in gaming history as you sip your cup of Joe from the Nintendo Game Boy coffee mug. With a retro design depicting a heart stopping Pokemon battle, it’s the ideal way for any gamer to get their day started.

Fallout fans will now be able to own their very own Pip-Boy 3000. This stunningly detailed prop features a lightweight Styrofoam design, covered with wood putty and acrylic paint to achieve a realistic appearance – just don’t count on it to provide any useful information.

Accent your outfit with the wings scarf and create the illusion you’ve sprouted a pair of glorious wings overnight. The majestic feather wing design on the scarf is accented by a stunning vintage green backdrop great for complementing a variety of looks.

Pay homage to your favorite horror flick mass murderer with the Jason hockey mask spoon. Ideal for the deranged cereal killer in your family, this quirky item features Jason’s iconic hockey mask skillfully sculpted onto the back of the spoon.

This Halloween season, give into your Dark Side and hit the streets wearing the Star Wars Darth Revan costume. This handmade costume includes a detailed mask, flexible form-fitting torso armor – sensitivity to the Force sold separately.

Embody the most fearsome villain in the city by dressing up in the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Shredder helmet. It features the iconic blade shaped helmet design in addition to a custom mouth guard to complete the look of the dreaded Shredder.

Give your room a macabre ambiance with the skull chair. Designed to look like a human skull, the chair features a realistic wrap-around graphic and comes with a movable jaw piece that lifts up to reveal a comfy and cozy resting spot.

Conquer the open skies in a way you never thought possible by strapping on a pair of mechanical wings. These high-tech wings come with brilliant LED lighting accents at the tips and can extend to four and a half feet wide with the flick of a switch.

Get the piece of mind you deserve by entrusting your home’s security to the metal RoboCop statue. At a commanding 8’2″, this fully metallic work of art looms over your yard and stands in a menacing pose to quickly deter any would be intruders from your home.

Immortalize yourself in your dorkiest of fantasies by placing yourself in your favorite games, cartoons, and movies with the personalized geeky portraits. At last, you’ll finally see what you would look like with pointy elf ears or battling on some far off alien planet.

Transform yourself into a fun loving fairy with the Tinkerbell costume wig. When paired with a pixie styled green dress and a pair of darling fairy wings, the only thing you’ll be missing from this is the magical fairy dust.

Complete the look of Pallet town’s most famous trainer with the Pokemon Ash cosplay costume. Equipped with Ash’s signature green fingerless gloves and iconic red and white baseball cap you’ll have everything you need to begin your journey – Pikachu sold separately.

Look fiercer than ever by accessorizing with the predator claw rings. While the intriguing style does little to help in the love department, the unique design transforms your dainty fingers into deadly weapons no one will want to mess with.

Spend some quality time with the Autobots by adding the giant Transformer to your backyard’s landscape. This colossal statue stands at nearly six and a half feet tall and features a powerful and intricately designed body made from recycled materials.

Treat your fellow ravers to a wild light show on your face by wearing the rainbow light up sunglasses. Made using the classic and always fashionable Wayfarer model, they come outfitted with brightly colored neon lights that run along the entire frame.

Achieve inner peace while adding a touch color to your home’s decor with the red maple bonsai tree kit. The life giving kit comes with everything necessary to grow your very own miniature tree – making it an ideal gift for any member of the family.

Brighten up everyone’s night when you show up wearing these chic light up cowgirl boots. This custom made pair of boots come outfitted with dozens of tiny lights that shine bright and will get you noticed wherever you go. Yeehaw!

Proclaim yourself the fairest maiden at the party when you show up dressed in the Snow White vinyl costume. This handmade ensemble is tailored for the perfect fit, accented with vivid colors and intricate detailing to help you pull off the look of this gorgeous maiden.

Get ready to raid Pandora and take Comic-Con by storm when you show up in the Avatar amp suit costume. The outfit transforms your puny body into a mechanized weapon of destruction designed to strike fear in the hearts of all indigenous life forms.

Bask in the warm glow of decomposing flesh by lighting up some melting zombie candles. Nothing sets the mood quite like snuggling with your significant other, lighting a zombie’s head on fire and watching him melt away over the course of several hours.

He said NO to drugs, brought Gorbachev and the sinister U.S.S.R. down to their knees, and invented Reaganomics. Now you can show your patriotism by commemorating the greatness of the 40th president with the Ronald Reagan riding a velociraptor painting.

Scare the costumes off trick-or-treaters that approach your home with help from the Venus flytrap Halloween decoration. Unlike their smaller cousins, these mutant sized Venus flytraps are equipped with gigantic razor sharp teeth and a monstrous protruding tongue.

Take your costume to infinity and beyond when you show up dressed in this amazingly detailed Buzz Lightyear getup. With features like a custom space helmet and deployed wings on the back, you’ll look like an exact replica of the iconic toy and movie character.

Morph into your favorite crime fighting reptile as you stay warm with the Ninja Turtles hoodie. This custom made hoodie provides a comfortable loose fit and is accented with professionally sewn fleece appliques to complete the look of these mutant turtles.

Rocket off to dreamland in comfort and style on the galaxy bed covers. These handmade satin covers feature a dazzling image of the universe printed onto the surface of the comforter and pillow cases so that you’re surrounded by the cosmos as you slumber.

Think of the Harry Potter iPhone case as a stylish patronus that guards your phone against scratches instead of Dementors. Made in the likeness of the famed wizard, the case features his classic specks, lighting shaped scar and his stylish Gryffindor scarf.

Provide a little flair for any dull room by hanging the stained glass dragon suncatcher. This handmade sculpture – inspired by winged beasts from Game of Thrones – projects incredible visual effects onto the walls as sunlight passes through it.

Leave your competition speechless and wow the audience by performing your routine in the crystalized leotard. This bejeweled garment provides a comfortable fit while its bright and sparking accents ensure you remain the center of attention.

Wreak havoc across <del>Termina</del> your home town by channeling the powerful dark magic of the wearable Zelda Majora’s mask. This handmade item is an exact replica of the mask from the game and features fabric tie straps and foam blocks for a comfortable fit.

Glitter switchplate covers are the ideal way to give your plain home a <del>tasteless</del> fabulous makeover without breaking the bank. Every inch of these custom switchplates feature a luxurious glitter coating designed to turn them into the focal point of any room.

titleEN: Crazy Cat Lady Family Car Sticker
content: Show the world how much you love your feline family with the crazy cat lady family car sticker. This handmade vinyl sticker is available in various vibrant colors so that you can proudly show off your ever growing clowder of kitty cats in a comical way.

Keep your arrows organized while looking the part of a medieval warrior by storing them inside the archeress leather quiver. This custom quiver features intricate brass accents and comes with a leather strap so you can comfortably carry the quiver on your back.

While you wouldn’t want to color with them, these are definitely the crayons you’ve been looking for. Each crayon features a hand-carved miniature sculpture of classic Star Wars characters like C-3P0, R2-D2, and Lord Vader himself.

Become your city’s very own symbol of hope by donning the Batman Dark Knight costume. This amazingly detailed costume is hand tailored and boasts all the body armor and accessories necessary to convincingly pull off the caped crusader look. I’M BATMAN.

titleEN: Home Is Where The Weed At
content: Nothing says home sweet home like plopping down on the sofa, lighting one up and admiring the “Home Is Where The Weed At” sign. This quaint embroidery is handmade with <del>THC</del> TLC in every stitch and adds to the homey environment of the house.

Your favorite Hylian characters have crossed over into unfamiliar lands and its left them a bit pixelated. The Legend of Zelda Minecraft figurines take these beloved characters and gives them an awesome 8-bit makeover using brightly colored beads.

Give your tiny rodent the gift of flight when you outfit him with the steampunk winged guinea pig armor. This custom armor is designed to comfortably fit your guinea pig while a pair of graceful leather and brass wings majestically spread above.

titleEN: Super Mario Bros Brick Planter Box
content: Give your garden a power-up with the Super Mario Bros brick planter box. The planter features a wood burned question mark symbol and brick wall design that wraps around the entire planter, making it an ideal place for gamers to grow their own magic mushrooms.

I am Groot, I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot. I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot, I am Groot – I am Groot I am Groot – I am Groot. I am Groot I am Groot; I am Groot I am Groot, I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot I am Groot!

While it may not offer much protection, the Zelda Hylian shield pillow delivers the comfort you crave after a stressful day of smashing pots and rummaging for rupees. Handmade in the image of Link’s iconic shield, it’s ideal for any gamer’s bedroom.

Achieve inner piece from the comfort of home with the ancient Buddha Zen garden terrarium. This Buddha sits in the middle of a peaceful garden overrun by growing vegetation that together creates a tranquil setting for you to meditate in front of.

Turn that pile of useless hoarded crap into a beautiful work of art with this personalized skull sculpture made from your own belongings! You can send just about anything lying around the house from old watches to trinkets, and have it used in the creation of the skull.

Ensure your day has a 99.9% rate of good luck by keeping the Heisenberg Buddha figurine by your side. This pudgy figurine encompasses the best from both worlds – balancing Heinsenberg’s aggressive ambition with the Buddha’s patience and wisdom.

As the overlord of the house, your cat expects nothing but the best and you must abide by his wishes for fresh drinking water by installing this water drinking fountain. No opposable thumbs required – your cat only needs to stand up on two paws to reach the fresh water.

Provide A-1 catering for Malibu Stacy’s next soiree by ensuring the staff serve mini clay food. These miniature entrees are handmade and expertly decorated to resemble real food. It’s guaranteed to take your daughter’s playtime to the next level.

When your <del>power level</del> RPM is over 9000 – handle it like a Super Saiyan with the Dragon Ball Z shift knob. A perfect addition for the car of any anime fan, it replaces your boring old shift knob with Goku’s iconic four star Dragon Ball.

Accessorize your feet when going sans footwear with the ivory barefoot sandals. These custom made sandals are skillfully woven from organic cotton and fit comfortably whether you decide to wear them with or without shoes.

Join the prestigious ranks of the Green Lantern the moment you put on this sterling silver Green Lantern replica ring. This handmade collector’s item displays the iconic lantern symbol and can be fully customized with either yellow gold, white gold or silver.

Indulge your unresolved childhood issues while spicing up your love life riding atop the BDSM rocking horse. Built to handle all types of erotic punishment, she waits patiently for you to jump on and ride her back and forth as hard you as can for as long as you can!

Make your child’s playroom a bit more incredible with the LEGO head wall clock. This jolly LEGO man always has a smile on his face as he informs you of the current time while simultaneously adding some unique playfulness to the rooms decor.

Take a fashion tip from the caped crusader and opt for all black accessories such as the Batman hair bow. With its unique bat shaped contour, the hair bow works perfectly for placing a little bit of Bruce Wayne flare onto your outfit.

Host an orgy of relaxation in your backyard when you install the mega hammock! This gargantuan hammock – at what point is this not classified as a tarp? – is custom made out of a tough bonded nylon thread and is built to handle several people all at once.

Bring a little piece of the wizard world into your boring old muggle life with the Harry Potter themed Monopoly. The special edition Monopoly game comes in a distinguished wooden chest and is filled with all the magical characters and places from the series.

Unleash a fun mini celebration with a single quick release of the push-pop confetti. Upon pushing the stick at the base, an explosion of multi-colored confetti is shot into the air – making it an ideal item for celebrations of all kinds.

Hang out with the father of Gonzo journalism any time you want with the Hunter S. Thompson finger puppet. Equipped with his signature hat, vest, cigarette holder, and aviator shades, he’s ready for whatever drug and booze infused adventure you have in store.

It’s a common sight in any urban sprawl, but we guarantee you’ve never seen a shoe toss quite like this lamp. Inspired by the ubiquitous landmark, the lamp dangles off a telephone pole while lighting up the room with halogen bulbs inside the shoe.

Brighten up your day when you light up your carny food with the light up cotton candy sticks. These handmade treats – ideal for parties – offer a fun and eye-catching alternative to traditional lighting that children and drug addicts will love.

Pay homage to your favorite show as you protect your smartphone with the Iron Throne iPhone case. Inspired by the imposing throne of the king, the case comes with a gritty color scheme and protruding swords that’ll make you rethink placing it in your pockets.

Keep your hands toasty in true super hero fashion when you cozy up to the Iron Man crochet wristwarmers. With a custom design that pays homage to Tony Stark’s iconic suit, you’ll remain warm and fashionable all day long with this geeky accessory.

How terrifying would your childhood have been if you were told that the tooth fairy was a psychotic serial killer? Using legally acquired real human molars, the tooth fairy necklace is a truly morbid interpretation of the fabled fantasy figure who visits you while you sleep.
